org.jetel.component

Class CopyByNameMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.component.CopyByNameMapping

  • public class CopyByNameMapping
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple replacement for CustomizedRecordTransform in CTL wildcard mapping. Maps exactly one record to one record, exact matches have priority, then remaining input fields are mapped one by one to the first unmapped case-insensitively matching output field, respectively.
